msgstr "élkezelés"

#: ../src/iop/diffuse.c:1751
msgid ""
"increase or decrease the sharpness of the highest frequencies.\n"
"can be used to keep details after blooming,\n"
"for standalone sharpening set speed to negative values."
msgstr ""
